If a major incident does not exist, an IT agent can directly create a major incident candidate from the Create Major Incident Candidate module in the navigator. 

The incident form opens from the Major Incident Candidate template. You can update the template to prefill other fields on the form.

The incident form contains the Major Incident section, and the Major incident state is set to Proposed.
